title: UFOs - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 7/5/22

description:
George Noory and UFO researcher Richard Lawrence discuss the continued push for world governments to disclose what they know about aliens visiting Earth, whether they come from other planets or other dimensions, and if they could already control our planet with their advanced technology.
